# tf.to_complex128

``` python
tf.to_complex128(
    x,
    name='ToComplex128'
)
```



Defined in [`tensorflow/python/ops/math_ops.py`](https://www.github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.10/tensorflow/python/ops/math_ops.py).

Casts a tensor to type `complex128`.

#### Args:

* <b>`x`</b>: A `Tensor` or `SparseTensor`.
* <b>`name`</b>: A name for the operation (optional).


#### Returns:

A `Tensor` or `SparseTensor` with same shape as `x` with type `complex128`.


#### Raises:

* <b>`TypeError`</b>: If `x` cannot be cast to the `complex128`.
